wiki.content: Written by: A. Lee, B. Moody, and D. Hodges The fourth and final single from the album Fallen. The song focuses upon how celebrities portray false images, and how these implement unrealistic ideals for the rest of the public to follow. The unifying theme of the video is that they are merely peddling lies. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
